query:
UPDATE admin_menus SET path = CASE 
  WHEN path = '/dashboard' THEN '/admin/dashboard'
  WHEN path = '/countries' THEN '/admin/countries'
  WHEN path = '/catalogo' THEN '/admin/catalogo'
  WHEN path = '/clientes' THEN '/admin/clientes'
  WHEN path = '/affiliates' THEN '/admin/affiliates'
  WHEN path = '/apis' THEN '/admin/apis'
  WHEN path = '/api-performance' THEN '/admin/api-performance'
  WHEN path = '/payment-settings' THEN '/admin/payment-settings'
  WHEN path = '/auditoria' THEN '/admin/auditoria'
  WHEN path = '/financial' THEN '/admin/financial'
  WHEN path = '/settings' THEN '/admin/settings'
  ELSE path
END
WHERE path NOT LIKE '/admin/%'
